                <div class="flowchart-item p-4 rounded-lg text-center shadow-md"><strong>入力データ</strong><br>(テキスト, 画像)</div>
                <div class="flowchart-arrow text-4xl transform md:-translate-y-1 md:rotate-0 rotate-90">→</div>
                <div class="flowchart-item p-4 rounded-lg text-center shadow-md"><strong>AIによるベクトル化</strong><br>(意味を数値に変換)</div>
